{"tid":1660069,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"重溫：警員朱振國被斬至植物人案 及 警員梁成恩被案","createTime":"2019-10-17T09:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T12:50:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5bcea580c9a91282c81a28fb6897f74c1b7a98e4","tid":1660069,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:52:46.000Z","msg":"世事既嘢真係好難講, 都係買重保險穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/YRqdqhq.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警員朱振國巡邏  遭兇徒割頸成植物人</span></span></strong><br />\nSOURCE:<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/即時-香港-當年今日-05年警員朱振國巡邏-遭兇徒割頸成植物人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5-05%E5%B9%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%87%E5%BE%92%E5%89%B2%E9%A0%B8%E6%88%90%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9%E4%BA%BA&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAYpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=feed4c20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5-05%E5%B9%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%B1%E6%8C%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%B7%A1%E9%82%8F-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%87%E5%BE%92%E5%89%B2%E9%A0%B8%E6%88%90%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9%E4%BA%BA&h=6bb370fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/即時-香港-當年今日-05年警員朱振國巡邏-遭兇徒割頸成植物人</a><br />\n<br />\n事發在當日早上8時半，警員朱振國當值早更，單獨外出巡邏，當巡至保安道巿政大廈對開時，發現男子廖智勇行為閃縮，遂上前截查。正當朱向電台查詢廖是否通緝犯之際，廖突然從身上拔出一把六吋長生果刀，刺向朱左邊頸部，並傷及大動脈致血流不止。廖傷人後即拔足狂奔，朱則負傷尾隨追趕，並用手按着傷口，但至50米外，終告不支倒地，而兇徒在逃出10米外，轉入巿政大廈的橫巷，並棄下利刀不知所終。在當日下午1時許，廖在太子地鐵站向一名巡警自首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1490000/1490273/copy20080219128_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1490000%2F1490273%2Fcopy20080219128_1024_1024.jpg&h=6f2045fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兇徒近距開槍  設局埋伏  轟頂殺梁成恩</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20070309/img/a20309a_big.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fnews%2F20070309%2Fimg%2Fa20309a_big.jpg&h=ce577b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180313/_2018031313190987779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180313%2F_2018031313190987779.jpg&h=aae898e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發當日，梨木樹警署報案室接到一名男子致電﹐表示在石桃樓一個單位有噪音滋擾﹐於是派梁成恩獨自前往調查。該單位住有一對母子，但事發時均外出，亦無法追查電話來源。當梁等候上級指示期間﹐就遭兇徒襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n享年24歲的梁成恩，在2002年獲追頒銀英勇勳章，遺體永久安葬浩園。"},{"pid":"ff06b973c9d99cb0fd8bca07ca283c312adcd216","tid":1660069,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c52c1bfe3756197845cd3d1a03e44d02fac3050f","tid":1660069,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY0B6sp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY0B6sp.jpg&h=c862b749&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a9b2a66a090f587d7760d11545086c23fa8937","tid":1660069,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全部同我入嚟支持民記</span></strong> <br />\n<code>[第二十次民間記者會]</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659956\" 